# Host-generated runtime state — never bake this into the image. It reflects
# whoever last ran the app locally (LLM provider/model choice, saved
# connections, dashboards, snapshots, usage history), not a fresh install.
# Found the hard way: a stale db/llm_config.json selecting a model that was
# never pulled into the bundled Ollama container caused silent 404s on every
# AI query. The image should only ship the static seed databases in db/
# (chinook.db, main.db, northwind.db, samples/) — everything below is
# per-deployment state, generated fresh by each container/volume instead.
db/llm_config.json
db/connections.json
db/dashboards.json
db/snapshots.json
db/usage_metrics.json
db/snapshots/
